<!DOCTYPE concept PUBLIC "-//OASIS//DTD DITA Concept//EN" "concept.dtd" []>
<concept xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" id="changing-the-target-of-external-xref" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="urn:oasis:names:tc:dita:xsd:concept.xsd:1.1">
  <title>Changing the Target of External Xref</title>
  <conbody>
    <p id="change-target-of-external-xref-intro">You can change the target of an external xref to another external target.</p>
    <p> This can be done one of these ways:<ul>
        <li>
          <p><xref href="changing-the-target-of-external-xref-to-another-external-target-in-an-existing-document.xml">Change the target of the external xref to another external target in an existing document</xref>.</p>
          <p conref="changing-the-target-of-external-xref-to-another-external-target-in-an-existing-document.xml#changing-the-target-of-external-xref-to-another-external-target-in-an-existing-document/change-target-of-external-xref-intro"/>
        </li>
        <li>
          <p><xref href="changing-the-target-of-external-xref-to-another-external-target-in-a-newly-created-document.xml">Change the target of the external xref to another external target in a newly-created document</xref>.</p>
          <p conref="changing-the-target-of-external-xref-to-another-external-target-in-a-newly-created-document.xml#changing-the-target-of-external-xref-to-another-external-target-in-a-newly-created-document/change-target-of-external-xref-intro"/>
        </li>
      </ul></p>
  </conbody>
</concept>
